This versatile Davis artist is a renowned ceramic sculptor as well as a musician. Her figurative sculptures are shown at the John Natsoulas Art Gallery John Natsoulas Gallery. She studied art at UC Davis with Robert Arneson, Manual Neri and Wayne Thiebaud. She is also in the band COLD SHOT. They had the distinction of performing at the 2006 Martin Luther King Jr. holiday remembrance. See her web page at http://www.renemartucci.com www.renemartucci.com.
